venue.name: Temple Of Olympian Zeus (Ναός Ολυμπίου Διός)

tip.text: Clean and spacious rooms with free breakfast, fast wifi, free croissant and an electric kettle. All these for an affordable price :)
Spacious, modern, and clean rooms! Really love this place. Surprised that they have a "heated" feature in the bathroom to keep you warm after showering. 👍
Food's not bad. Warm and cosy ambience :)
Beef burger was quite nice. Cosy and eccentric indoors as well. Pity there wasn't an English menu.

tip.text: Tasty breakfast with fantastic Ham & Cheese omelette. Pity the breakfast menu is quite pricey compared to other cafes nearby.
Steak with strawberry cheese sauce is tasty. Cod is superb as well. Staff displayed excellent service as they were kind enough to split one bowl of soup to two bowls to make it easier for sharing :)
Cosy cafe with fresh bread. Good for take aways or quick bite.
The ribs are finger licking good! 👍
